      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "functional:\n1. client can query top k videos of all time\n2. tumbling windows of 1(hour, day, month) and all time \nupto a max of 1k results\n\nout of scope:\n1. arbitary time periods\n2. arbitary starting/end points. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "functional:\n1. client can query top k videos of all time\n2. tumbling windows of 1(hour, day, month) and all time \nupto a max of 1k results\n\nout of scope:\n1. arbitary time periods\n2. arbitary starting/end points. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
